OL,7,FMore than #125k has been raised in 48
OL,8,Fhours for a serving Gloucestershire
OL,9,FPolice officer who lost his wife and
OL,10,Fchildren in a house fire on Boxing Day.
OL,12,FThe fundraising page was set up to
OL,13,Fsupport him after the fire devastated
OL,14,Fthe home on Brimscombe Hill near
OL,15,FStroud in the early hours of Friday,
OL,16,F26 December.
OL,18,FIt explains: "(He) is now facing an
OL,19,Funimaginable period of grief alongside
OL,20,Fthe very real and immediate practical
OL,21,Freality of having nothing left.
