OL,7,F"This fund has been set up to help
OL,8,Fsupport them with the practical needs
OL,9,Fhe's facing now and in the months
OL,10,Fahead - including emergency
OL,11,Faccommodation, clothing and
OL,12,Fessentials, time away from work and
OL,13,Fthe many unexpected costs that arise
OL,14,Fduring a period like this.
OL,16,F"Right now, the most important thing
OL,17,Fis that he can focus on getting
OL,18,Fthrough each day, without the added
OL,19,Fpressure of financial or practical
OL,20,Fworries.
