OL,7,F"Any contribution, no matter how
OL,8,Fsmall, will make a meaningful
OL,9,Fdifference. If you're unable to
OL,10,Fdonate, sharing this page is just as
OL,11,Fappreciated - there is no pressure.
OL,13,F"Thank you for your kindness,
OL,14,Fgenerosity and support at an
OL,15,Fincredibly difficult time."
