OL,7,FAt a press briefing on Monday, 29
OL,8,FDecember, Ian Fletcher, Detective
OL,9,FSuperintendent at Gloucestershire
OL,10,FPolice, confirmed that when crews
OL,11,Farrived at the property, the fire was
OL,12,Fwell-established and the husband was
OL,13,Foutside the house trying to gain entry.
OL,15,FHe desperately attempted to rescue his
OL,16,Fwife, who was in her 30s, and two
OL,17,Fchildren ` a girl aged seven and a
OL,18,Ffour-year-old boy ` but was beaten
OL,19,Fback by the severity of the blaze.
